Prisma

Tenant Name {{element.tenant_name}} Client ID {{element.client_id}} Client Secret {{element.client_secret}} API Token {{element.api_token}} Author {{element.author}} Created At {{element.created_at}}
import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { AuthService } from '../auth.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-prisma', templateUrl: './prisma.component.html', styleUrls: ['./prisma.component.scss'] }) export class PrismaComponent implements OnInit { prismaData: any; displayedColumns: string[] = ['tenant_name', 'client_id', 'client_secret', 'tsg_id', 'author', 'created_at']; constructor(private http: HttpClient, private authService: AuthService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.fetchPrismaData(); } fetchPrismaData() { this.http.get('http://localhost:8000/api/v1/prisma').subscribe( (data: any) => { this.prismaData = data; }, (error) => { console.error('Error fetching Prisma data:', error); } ); } }
